Therefore, my conclusion, based on my thorough analysis, is that the current administrative unit for the old address "Xã An Định, Huyện Tuy An, Tỉnh Phú Yên" is now **"Xã Tuy An Bắc"**, within the province of **"Tỉnh Đắk Lắk"**.
